            <img class="arrow left" src="/images/growth-enhancer/left-arrow.png" alt="">
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="control right-arrow">
            <img class="arrow right" src="/images/growth-enhancer/right-arrow.png" alt="">
          </a>
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <strong class="value-heading">A company of friends</strong>
            <p class="value-desc">We have fun while working, often hang out together and go to the seaside. Although sometimes the Atlantic separates us, we are always there for one another.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <strong class="value-heading">Constant learning</strong>
            <p class="value-desc">We recognize our weaknesses and are committed to self-improvement. We ask for feedback, but are even more interested in what others can teach or show us.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="controls circles">
          <a href="#" class="circle"></a>
          <a href="#" class="circle active"></a>
          <a href="#" class="circle"></a>
          <a href="#" class="circle"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section -white -padding-m menu-open growth-enhancer-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>A day in our office</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <img src="/images/growth-enhancer/pie-chart.svg" alt="Pie Chart">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section -green -padding-l bizdev-section why-join-us" id="values">
    <div class="container values list">
      <h2>Why join Enhancv?</h2>
      <div class="row list-item">
