          <p class="value-desc">Neil Patel&#8195;/&#8195;Sean Ellis&#8195;/&#8195;Rand Fishkin&#8195;/&#8195;Brian Dean&#8195;/&#8195;Paul Graham&#8195;/&#8195;David Heinemeier Hansson</p>
        </div>
